[TITLE]
Compound rule conditions — AND/OR logic

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    0    50
J2    0    30

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    0

[TANKS]
; ID   Elev  Init  Min  Max  Diam  0
T1     100   5     0    10   50    0

[PIPES]
P1    J1    J2    500    12    100    0    Open
P2    J2    T1    500    12    100    0    Open

[PUMPS]
PMP1    R1    J1    HEAD C1

[CURVES]
C1    0    300
C1    500    200
C1    1000    50

[RULES]
; Compound AND: pump on when tank is low AND pressure at J1 is below threshold
RULE 1
IF NODE T1 LEVEL BELOW 3.0
AND NODE J1 PRESSURE BELOW 200
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS OPEN
PRIORITY 2

; Pump off when tank is full
RULE 2
IF NODE T1 LEVEL ABOVE 8.0
THEN LINK PMP1 STATUS IS CLOSED
PRIORITY 1

[OPTIONS]
Units    GPM
Headloss    H-W

[TIMES]
Duration    48:00
Hydraulic Timestep    1:00
Report Timestep    1:00

[END]
